      • builderOutTradeNo

        public PayRefundQueryParamChain builderOutTradeNo(String outTradeNo)
        !!This Is An Indispensable Parameter When The Order Is Paid, The Incoming Merchant Order Number And The AliPay Transaction Number Can Not Be Empty At The Same Time. OutTradeNo, OutRequestNo If There Is A Priority OutTradeNo At The Same Time

        !!这是不可缺参数 订单支付时传入的商户订单号,和支付宝交易号不能同时为空. OutTradeNo,OutRequestNo如果同时存在优先取OutTradeNo

        参数:
        outTradeNo - outTradeNo
        返回:
        PayRefundQueryParamChain

      • builderOutRequestNo

        public PayRefundQueryParamChain builderOutRequestNo(String outRequestNo)
        !!This Is An Indispensable Parameter When Requesting The Refund Interface, The Incoming Refund Request Number. If It Is Not Passed In At The Time Of Refund Request, The Value Is The External Transaction Number At The Time Of Transaction Creation

        !!这是不可缺参数 请求退款接口时,传入的退款请求号, 如果在退款请求时未传入,则该值为创建交易时的外部交易号

        参数:
        outRequestNo - outRequestNo
        返回:
        PayRefundQueryParamChain

      • builderOrgPid

        public PayRefundQueryParamChain builderOrgPid(String orgPid)
        It Is Useful In The Bank To Bank Mode. Please Do Not Use It In Other Scenarios; Through This Parameter, The Double Link Specifies The PID Of The Acquirer Of The Exchange To Be Queried;

        银行间联模式下有用,其它场景请不要使用: 双联通过该参数指定需要查询的交易所属收单机构的PID;

        参数:
        orgPid - orgPid
        返回:
        PayRefundQueryParamChain
